@startuml
package "Server (src/)" {
  [main.py] #--> [api.py]
  [main.py] #--> [database.py]
  [main.py] #--> [models.py]
  [main.py] --> [PostgreSQL]
  [api.py] --> [models.py]
  [api.py] --> [database.py]
  [main.py] --> [Static Files]
}

package "Client (static/)" {
  [index.html] --> [index.js]
  [index.html] --> [header.html]
  [index.html] --> [header.js]
  [cabinet.html] --> [cabinet.js]
  [cabinet.html] --> [header.html]
  [cabinet.html] --> [header.js]
}

[Static Files] --> [Client (static/)]
[Client (static/)] --> [Browser]
[Browser] --> [main.py] : HTTP Requests (e.g., /repairs/estimates)

[main.py] --> [FastAPI]
[database.py] --> [SQLAlchemy]
[SQLAlchemy] --> [PostgreSQL]

note right of [main.py]
  Initializes FastAPI, mounts static files,
  includes API routes, and sets up database.
end note

note right of [api.py]
  Defines API endpoints (/repairs/*) for
  authentication, estimates, and data management.
end note

note right of [models.py]
  SQLAlchemy models for Clients, Users,
  Premises, WorkTypes, Estimates, etc.
end note

note right of [database.py]
  Configures sync and async database engines
  and session factories for PostgreSQL.
end note

note right of [index.html]
  Main page with estimate calculator form,
  interacts with API via index.js.
end note

note right of [cabinet.html]
  User dashboard for viewing saved estimates,
  interacts with API via cabinet.js.
end note

note right of [header.html]
  Common header for navigation,
  loaded by index.html and cabinet.html.
end note

note right of [header.js]
  Handles authentication status and
  navigation tab visibility.
end note

@enduml